---
interface Props {
  spotsTotal: number;
  ctaHref: string;
}

const { spotsTotal, ctaHref } = Astro.props;
const spotsFormatted = String(spotsTotal).padStart(2, "0");
---

<section class="section founding" id="fundadores" aria-labelledby="found-h2">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="tray">
      <span class="serial">§ 06 / Cupos fundadores</span>
      <span class="meta">Precio de validación · cierra al llenarse</span>
    </div>

    <div class="founding-grid">
      <aside class="cupos" aria-label="Cupos fundadores disponibles">
        <div class="cupos-num"><span>{spotsFormatted}</span></div>
        <div class="cupos-label">Cupos fundadores<br />disponibles</div>
        <div class="cupos-status">
          <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Abierto · Q2 2026
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Oferta fundadora</p>
        <h2 id="found-h2" class="found-h2">Dos cuentas iniciales a <em>precio de validación</em>.</h2>
        <p class="lede found-lede">
          Estamos abriendo dos cuentas para documentar resultados con el nicho dental. Precio reducido a cambio del
          caso: tú llegas antes que la competencia, nosotros demostramos el modelo.
        </p>

        <div class="founding-detail">
          <div>
            <div class="k">Fee fundador</div>
            <div class="v">$950.000<span class="unit">/mes</span></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="k">Setup</div>
            <div class="v">$500.000<span class="unit">único</span></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="k">Pauta</div>
            <div class="v alt">Aparte</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="note found-note">
          Al cerrarse los dos cupos, el precio sube a la banda estándar de $1.150.000–$1.200.000/mes. Sin excepciones.
        </p>

        <div class="founding-cta">
          <a
            href={ctaHref}
            class="btn"
            id="founding-cta-btn"
            data-analytics-event="cta_click"
            data-analytics-location="founding"
          >
            Solicita una revisión gratis <svg class="arrow" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-arrow"></use></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .found-h2 {
    margin-top: 0.65rem;
  }
  .found-lede {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .found-note {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .founding-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .founding-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 320px) minmax(0, 1fr);
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .cupos {
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bone-2);
  }
  .cupos-num {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 9vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 0.85;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .cupos-num span {
    color: var(--vermilion);
  }
  .cupos-label {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--t-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--graphite);
  }
  .cupos-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--t-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--ink);
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--bone-line);
  }
  .cupos-status .dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--vermilion);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2.4s var(--ease-out) infinite;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .founding-detail {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--bone-line);
  }
  .founding-detail > div {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--bone-line);
  }
  .founding-detail > div:last-child {
    border-right: 0;
  }
  .founding-detail .k {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--t-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .founding-detail .v {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: var(--t-2xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }
  .founding-detail .v.alt {
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--vermilion);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .founding-detail .v .unit {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--t-xs);
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-left: 0.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .founding-detail {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .founding-detail > div {
      border-right: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bone-line);
    }
    .founding-detail > div:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }
  }

  .founding-cta {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
